prompt.title: Embedding for Dangers of Cheap Costume Jewelry
prompt.content: In the current period of economic crisis, fraudulent and health-damaging costume jewelry is increasingly appearing on the market as people try to save money. Korálky Katlas has prepared a summary of things to watch out for when buying finished costume jewelry and jewelry components, based on problems and scams reported by their customers in the Czech Republic and abroad.
